name: structured_v9_loop_for_adds_branch_value_2_times
section: control-loop-mutation-v9
args: p:Bool a:Int b:Int c:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: for loop must preserve loop-carried accumulator state across 2 iterations with branch-selected increment.
law: (= (with [acc {a}] (do (for 2 (set! acc (+ acc (if {p} {b} {c})))) acc)) (+ {a} (* (if {p} {b} {c}) 2)))
